messages.messageBody: Liked “Also, while I have you, I wanted to ask a favor. Have you left us a Google review yet? We survive on our Google reviews. It'd mean the world to us if you left us a review. We aim to get 800 Google reviews by the end of the year. Here is the link to it: https://tinyurl.com/reviewullrichinsurance. It might take just a minute. If you could do this, it would be amazing. If you can’t, it’s okay too. Thanks, Krissey!”
Liked “Of course! They don't have a nurse discount specifically but they did add a bit of discount for changing your occupation to being a nurse.”
